---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import CtaBand from "../../components/CtaBand.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Why SYAG — Take Full Control of Your Security Operations"
  description="SYAG replaces paper logs, scattered tools, and manual coordination with one system built for managing guards, incidents, visitors, and site security."
>

  <!-- ─── HERO ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 space-y-8">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
      <span class="badge-pill">
        <span class="badge-dot"></span>
        Why SYAG
      </span>
    </div>
    <h1 class="quartr-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-semibold text-white max-w-3xl leading-[1.05]">
      Take full control of your <span style="color:#ff8a3c">security operations</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="max-w-xl text-base leading-relaxed text-white/55">
      SYAG replaces paper logs, scattered tools, and manual coordination with one system built specifically for managing guards, incidents, visitors, and site security.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 pt-2">
      <a href="/demo" class="rounded-full bg-white px-6 py-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-black hover:bg-white/90 transition-colors">
        Request a Demo
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── DIVIDER RULE ─────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <div class="border-t border-white/[0.07]"></div>

  <!-- ─── THE PROBLEM ──────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-24 space-y-14">
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-white/40">The Problem</p>
      <h2 class="quartr-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-white max-w-2xl">
        Security operations today are fragmented
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.08] bg-white/[0.02] p-7 space-y-3 group hover:border-white/[0.14] transition-colors">
        <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-white/35">01</div>
        <p class="text-white font-medium text-sm leading-snug">Paper logs and manual records</p>
        <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Guards rely on handwritten sheets that get lost, filled incorrectly, or reviewed too late.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.08] bg-white/[0.02] p-7 space-y-3 group hover:border-white/[0.14] transition-colors">
        <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-white/35">02</div>
        <p class="text-white font-medium text-sm leading-snug">WhatsApp and phone calls</p>
        <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Supervisors depend on informal channels with no audit trail and no structured escalation.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.08] bg-white/[0.02] p-7 space-y-3 group hover:border-white/[0.14] transition-colors">
        <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-white/35">03</div>
        <p class="text-white font-medium text-sm leading-snug">Incidents recorded too late</p>
        <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">By the time an incident is documented, critical details are already missing or distorted.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.08] bg-white/[0.02] p-7 space-y-3 group hover:border-white/[0.14] transition-colors">
        <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-white/35">04</div>
        <p class="text-white font-medium text-sm leading-snug">No real-time visibility</p>
        <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">There is no clear view of what is happening across your site at any given moment.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── DIVIDER RULE ─────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <div class="border-t border-white/[0.07]"></div>

  <!-- ─── WHY SYAG ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-24 space-y-14">
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-white/40">The Solution</p>
      <h2 class="quartr-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-white max-w-2xl">
        Everything in one place — designed for how security teams actually work
      </h2>
      <p class="max-w-xl text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/55">
        Instead of managing operations across calls, spreadsheets, and disconnected tools, you run everything from a single system. See which guards are on duty, which patrols are completed, and who is inside your property — at any moment.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Bento grid of benefits -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">

      <!-- Wide card -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2 rounded-3xl border border-white/[0.08] bg-white/[0.02] p-8 space-y-5 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 rounded-full" style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(47,123,255,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%); transform: translate(30%, -30%);"></div>
        <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-white/35">01 — Built for security</p>
        <h3 class="quartr-heading text-xl font-semibold text-white">Purpose-built for security operations</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed max-w-md">
          SYAG is not a generic tool adapted for security — it is built for guards, patrols, incidents, and gate management. Every feature maps to how your operation actually runs.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-2 pt-2 flex-wrap">
          <span class="rounded-full border border-white/15 px-3 py-1 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/50">Guard Management</span>
          <span class="rounded-full border border-white/15 px-3 py-1 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/50">Patrol Tracking</span>
          <span class="rounded-full border border-white/15 px-3 py-1 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/50">Incident Response</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Tall card -->
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/[0.08] bg-white/[0.02] p-8 space-y-5 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-48 h-48 rounded-full" style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(53,224,255,0.05) 0%, transparent 70%); transform: translate(-30%, 30%);"></div>
        <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-white/35">02 — Live awareness</p>
        <h3 class="quartr-heading text-xl font-semibold text-white">Know what is happening as it happens</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed">
          See active guards, completed patrols, and live alerts — no waiting for reports or manual updates.
        </p>
        <!-- Live indicator widget -->
        <div class="mt-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.08] bg-white/[0.03] p-4 space-y-3">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-white/40">Live Status</span>
            <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#ff8a3c] shadow-[0_0_6px_rgba(255,138,60,0.7)]"></span>
              <span class="text-[10px] text-white/40">Active</span>
            </span>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-xs text-white/60">Guards on duty</span>
              <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-white">12</span>
            </div>
            <div class="h-px bg-white/[0.06]"></div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-xs text-white/60">Patrols completed</span>
              <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-white">8 / 10</span>
            </div>
            <div class="h-px bg-white/[0.06]"></div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-xs text-white/60">Open incidents</span>
              <span class="text-xs font-semibold" style="color:#ff8a3c">2</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Narrow card -->
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/[0.08] bg-white/[0.02] p-8 space-y-5">
        <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-white/35">03 — Field-ready</p>
        <h3 class="quartr-heading text-xl font-semibold text-white">Designed for guards in the field</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed">
          Guards scan checkpoints, report incidents, and complete tasks from a simple mobile app — no paperwork, no delays.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Wide card -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2 rounded-3xl border border-white/[0.08] bg-white/[0.02] p-8 space-y-5 relative overflow-hidden">
        <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-white/35">04 — Connected system</p>
        <h3 class="quartr-heading text-xl font-semibold text-white">Every module speaks to every other</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed max-w-md">
          Visitors, incidents, patrols, and alerts are all linked together. No switching between systems. No lost information.
        </p>
        <!-- Module pill row -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 pt-1">
          {["Visitors", "Incidents", "Patrols", "Guards", "Cameras", "IoT", "Assets"].map((m) => (
            <span class="rounded-full bg-white/[0.05] border border-white/[0.08] px-3 py-1.5 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/50">{m}</span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Full-width accountability card -->
      <div class="md:col-span-3 rounded-3xl border border-white/[0.08] bg-white/[0.02] p-8 md:p-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center gap-8">
        <div class="flex-1 space-y-4">
          <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-white/35">05 — Full accountability</p>
          <h3 class="quartr-heading text-xl font-semibold text-white">Track every action across your operation</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed max-w-md">
            Know who did what, when, and where. Every guard action, every incident update, every entry — timestamped and stored with full attribution.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 flex gap-6 md:gap-10">
          <div class="text-center space-y-1">
            <div class="quartr-heading text-3xl font-semibold text-white">100%</div>
            <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-white/40">Actions logged</div>
          </div>
          <div class="w-px bg-white/[0.08]"></div>
          <div class="text-center space-y-1">
            <div class="quartr-heading text-3xl font-semibold text-white">0</div>
            <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-white/40">Paper trails</div>
          </div>
          <div class="w-px bg-white/[0.08]"></div>
          <div class="text-center space-y-1">
            <div class="quartr-heading text-3xl font-semibold text-white">Real-time</div>
            <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-white/40">Visibility</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── DIVIDER RULE ─────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <div class="border-t border-white/[0.07]"></div>

  <!-- ─── BEFORE / AFTER ───────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-24 space-y-12">
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-white/40">Before &amp; After</p>
      <h2 class="quartr-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-white max-w-2xl">
        The difference is immediate
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">

      <!-- Without SYAG -->
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/[0.06] bg-white/[0.015] p-8 space-y-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full border border-white/20 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-white/30 text-xs">✕</span>
          </div>
          <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-white/35">Without SYAG</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          {[
            "Paper logs and manual records",
            "No clear view of daily operations",
            "Delayed incident response",
            "Scattered communication across tools",
            "No accountability or audit trail",
          ].map((item) => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-4 h-4 rounded-full border border-white/[0.12] flex items-center justify-center text-white/25 text-[9px]">—</span>
              <span class="text-sm text-white/40 leading-snug">{item}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- With SYAG -->
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/[0.12] bg-white/[0.03] p-8 space-y-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full border border-white/30 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-white/70 text-xs">✓</span>
          </div>
          <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-white/60">With SYAG</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          {[
            "Digital records and structured data",
            "Clear visibility across all sites",
            "Faster response and resolution",
            "One system for the entire operation",
            "Full audit trail and accountability",
          ].map((item) => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-white/[0.08] flex items-center justify-center text-white/60 text-[9px]">✓</span>
              <span class="text-sm text-white/75 leading-snug">{item}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── DIVIDER RULE ─────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <div class="border-t border-white/[0.07]"></div>

  <!-- ─── REAL SCENARIOS ───────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-24 space-y-12">
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-white/40">In Practice</p>
      <h2 class="quartr-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-white max-w-2xl">
        How it works in real situations
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4">

      <!-- Scenario 1 -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.08] bg-white/[0.02] p-6 md:p-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center gap-4 md:gap-0">
          <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center gap-3 md:gap-0">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 md:flex-1">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-white/[0.12] bg-white/[0.04] flex items-center justify-center text-white/50 text-xs flex-shrink-0">1</div>
              <span class="text-sm text-white/70">Visitor arrives at gate</span>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden md:block w-8 text-white/20 text-center">→</div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 md:flex-1">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-white/[0.12] bg-white/[0.04] flex items-center justify-center text-white/50 text-xs flex-shrink-0">2</div>
              <span class="text-sm text-white/70">Guard scans QR code</span>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden md:block w-8 text-white/20 text-center">→</div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 md:flex-1">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-white/[0.12] bg-white/[0.04] flex items-center justify-center text-white/50 text-xs flex-shrink-0">3</div>
              <span class="text-sm text-white/75 font-medium">Entry recorded instantly</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="md:ml-8 flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="rounded-full border border-white/15 px-3 py-1 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/40">Visitor Management</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Scenario 2 -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.08] bg-white/[0.02] p-6 md:p-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center gap-4 md:gap-0">
          <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center gap-3 md:gap-0">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 md:flex-1">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-white/[0.12] bg-white/[0.04] flex items-center justify-center text-white/50 text-xs flex-shrink-0">1</div>
              <span class="text-sm text-white/70">Patrol checkpoint missed</span>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden md:block w-8 text-white/20 text-center">→</div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 md:flex-1">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-white/[0.12] bg-white/[0.04] flex items-center justify-center text-white/50 text-xs flex-shrink-0">2</div>
              <span class="text-sm text-white/70">System flags it immediately</span>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden md:block w-8 text-white/20 text-center">→</div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 md:flex-1">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-white/[0.12] bg-white/[0.04] flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0" style="border-color:rgba(255,138,60,0.3)">
                <span class="text-[10px]" style="color:#ff8a3c">!</span>
              </div>
              <span class="text-sm font-medium" style="color:#ff8a3c">Supervisor notified</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="md:ml-8 flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="rounded-full border border-white/15 px-3 py-1 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/40">Patrol Monitoring</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Scenario 3 -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.08] bg-white/[0.02] p-6 md:p-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center gap-4 md:gap-0">
          <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center gap-3 md:gap-0">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 md:flex-1">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-white/[0.12] bg-white/[0.04] flex items-center justify-center text-white/50 text-xs flex-shrink-0">1</div>
              <span class="text-sm text-white/70">Incident reported in field</span>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden md:block w-8 text-white/20 text-center">→</div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 md:flex-1">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-white/[0.12] bg-white/[0.04] flex items-center justify-center text-white/50 text-xs flex-shrink-0">2</div>
              <span class="text-sm text-white/70">Assigned and tracked</span>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden md:block w-8 text-white/20 text-center">→</div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 md:flex-1">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-white/[0.12] bg-white/[0.04] flex items-center justify-center text-white/50 text-xs flex-shrink-0">3</div>
              <span class="text-sm text-white/75 font-medium">Resolved and logged</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="md:ml-8 flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="rounded-full border border-white/15 px-3 py-1 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/40">Incident Management</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── DIVIDER RULE ─────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <div class="border-t border-white/[0.07]"></div>

  <!-- ─── CLOSING STATEMENT ────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 space-y-6 text-center">
    <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-white/40">The Outcome</p>
    <h2 class="quartr-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold text-white max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-[1.1]">
      One system.<br/>Full control.
    </h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-white/50 max-w-md mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      SYAG gives you full control over your security operations — from the gate to the control room. You always know what is happening, who is responsible, and what needs attention.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── CTA ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <CtaBand
    headline="See SYAG in Action"
    primaryLabel="Request a Demo"
    primaryHref="/demo"
  />

</Layout>
